   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Emergency Fund COVID-19 for our elderly users</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In these difficult and complex times the elderlies are the most vulnerable population. We need your help TODAY to protect them. Hogar de Cristo welcomes more than 4,100 older adults in hostels, residences and home support programs and a significant part of the 15,000 people served by us who live on the streets are also elderlies. We are facing the 9th month of pandemic and your help is more needed than ever. Solidarity and empathy have proven to be the solution to get better out of these times.</narrative>
  </description>
